headline: Teradyne AI Data Center Venture Tests Growth Story Against Rich Valuation
summary: Teradyne (NasdaqGS:TER) and MultiLane have formed a joint venture to develop test solutions for AI data center equipment. The partnership focuses on high speed data connections that support AI and large scale cloud workloads. The joint venture targets test needs for next generation AI servers, networking gear, and optical connectivity. Teradyne, best known for semiconductor and electronics test equipment, is moving deeper into the plumbing of AI infrastructure through this joint effort with...
